import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"developer-quickstart"}}>{`Developer Quickstart`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="hr" components={components}></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"content-needed"}}>{`CONTENT NEEDED`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`creating a pod`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`configure your application profile
a. upload a logo (/profile/logo.zip)
b. add marketing copy (/profile.description)
c. add a subscription "scope"
d. preview your app in a demo app-store`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h4" components={components} props={{"id":"receiving-events"}}>{`Receiving Events`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Process overview`}<MDXTag name="ol" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`setup your app`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`user invites your app to receive subscription (send InviteAction) (you get an event)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`you accept the subscription invitation (send AcceptAction)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`you start getting messages`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Notification Wrapper`}<MDXTag name="ol" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`schema`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Subscription Scopes`}<MDXTag name="ol" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`explaination`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`example see `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://api.slack.com/events/app_rate_limited"}}>{`https://api.slack.com/events/app_rate_limited`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`link to /topics`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Change your inbox location`}<MDXTag name="ol" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol"></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h4" components={components} props={{"id":"publishing-events"}}>{`Publishing Events`}</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
